  line `9. Subs. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 120, for one year (w.e.f. 14-5-2016).`
  line
  line `10. Subs. by s. 120, ibid., for levied or has been short levied (w.e.f. 14-5-2016).`
  line
  line `11. Subs. by s. 120, ibid., for so levied (w.e.f. 14-5-2016).`
  line
  line `12. Subs by s. 120, ibid., for duty has not been levied or has been short levied (w.e.f. 14-5-2016).`
  line
  line `13. Subs. by Act 20 of 2015, s. 82, for twenty-five per cent. (w.e.f. 14-5-2015).`
  line
  line `14. Subs. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 120 for one year (w.e.f. 14-5-2016).`
  line
  line `15. Ins. by Act 13 of 2018, s. 63 (w.e.f. 28-3-2018).`
  line
  line `16. The words where it is possible to do so omitted by s. 63, ibid. (w.e.f. 28-3-2018).`
  line
  line `17. Ins. by Act 13 of 2018, s. 63 (w.e.f. 28-3-2018).`
  line
  line `18. Ins. by Act 14 of 2011, s. 2 (w.e.f. 16-9-2011).`
  line
  line `19. Subs. by Act 28 of 2016, s. 120, for not levied (w.e.f. 14-5-2016).`
