  string
  line `(1) The proper officer may, subject to any rules made`
  line `under sub-section (2), pass free of duty--`
  line
  line `(a) any article in the baggage of a passenger or a member of the crew in respect of which the said`
  line `officer is satisfied that it has been in his use for such minimum period as may be specified in the`
  line rules;
  line
  line `(b) any article in the baggage of a passenger in respect of which the said officer is satisfied that it`
