  line `crew for the purpose of clause (a) of sub-section (1);`
  line
  line `(b) the maximum value of any individual article and the maximum total value of all the articles`
  line `which may be passed free of duty under clause (b) of sub-section (1);`
  line
  line `(c) the conditions (to be fulfilled before or after clearance) subject to which any baggage may be`
