  string
  line `[Certain persons who have filed appeals to the Appellate Tribunal entitled to make`
  line `applications to the Settlement Commission.]Omitted by the Finance Act, 2007 (22 of 2007), s. 109 (w.e.f.`
  line `1-6-2007).`
